response.original_title: Desi Kisse (Na Umra Ki Seema Ho) - Part 1
response.overview: Ajay returns from Canada being married to an NRI, causing his old love, Reena, heartbreak. Ajay claims he married for business purposes and plans to divorce soon, keeping his plan a secret. But his plan is about to backfire as his wife, Jazz, gets drawn toward Ajay's father figure!
